snippet.title: PlayStation - Touhou Chinyuuki - Hafling Hearts!! (1996) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Touhou Chinyuuki: Hafling Hearts!! is an Adventure game, developed by Earthly Soft and published by Naxat Soft, which was released in Japan in 1996.
